### Variables
# All requests now point to the Gateway (Port 8082)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8082/api

# Using the static UUID from our fixed DataInitializer
@categoryId = 33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333
@elementId = e7fda372-c892-4156-9c32-988c8268ec64

### 1. Get All Categories
# Routed to Category Service (8080)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories

### 2. Create a Category
# Routed to Category Service (8080)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hardware"
}

### 3. Get All Elements in a Category
# Routed to Element Service (8081)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}/elements

### 4. Create an Element in a Category
# Routed to Element Service (8081)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}/elements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mechanical Keyboard",
  "price": 120.00
}

### 5. Get All Elements (Flat List)
# Routed to Element Service (8081)
GET {{baseUrl}}/elements

### 6. Delete an Element
# Routed to Element Service (8081)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/elements/{{elementId}}

### 7. Delete a Category (Triggers Cascade to Elements)
# Routed to Category Service (8080).
# Category Service then notifies Element Service (8081) via the internal Sync API.
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}